        "subject": "LU-16035 kfilnd: Don't call lnet_finalize in IRQ",
        "message": "LU-16035 kfilnd: Don't call lnet_finalize in IRQ\n\nWhen a timeout occurs, lnet_finalize() may be called in the timer\ncontext which is a softIRQ. This will cause LNet to panic. To prevent\nthis, when a timeout occurs, queue the timed out transaction for\nfuture processing on the kfilnd work queue.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nHPE-bug-id: LUS-10069\nSigned-off-by: Ian Ziemba <ian.ziemba@hpe.com>\nChange-Id: Ia51b18d3e7e904d28b71d2dcf48b500920f536cc\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
